# Upload File dengan JSON Request #

Sample Request

```
curl -X PUT \
  'http://localhost:8080/upload' \
  --header 'Accept: */*' \
  --header 'User-Agent: Thunder Client (https://www.thunderclient.com)' \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data-raw '{
  "name": "gps-config.png",
  "type": "image/png",
  "content": ""
}'
```

Response upload

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "filename": "23e61b3b-fe9d-4795-b2d1-94dd0783afa2.png",
  "size": 83319,
  "type": "image/png"
}
```

View file, browse ke `http://localhost:8080/download/23e61b3b-fe9d-4795-b2d1-94dd0783afa2.png`.
Sesuaikan url dengan `filename` yang ada di response upload.
